item.title: [Pi] Help please [Pi]
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

sk8rdude461:

I really feel like Team_Rocket could solve this, and you are just bullshitting us by saying he tried to help

No, I did try to help him. He couldn’t understand and apparently didn’t care enough to follow up on it, so I just stopped posting.

Import/Convert/Whatever else you decide to try. One quick trip to Oracle will give you a simple enough explanation of this error. You need to put forth an effort to follow up on this information yourself. This is a simple error when compared to others you will eventually be working out. How do you plan to solve future complications? You won’t be able to if you don’t take the initiative to learn yourself. You’ll be running to Mopar Forums every time something goes wrong.

P.S. Why are you working on adding Clipping for features if you’re stuck at finding Variables?
